title: Top 30 Country Jan 6, 2015
description:
Welcome to 2015! Very little has happened on the charts over the last few weeks as most radio stations were concentrating on their seasonal music. Not many labels release any singles this time of year either, so the chart is quite stagnant. One new song does appear, however from Easton Corbin. Here are the Top 30 US Country singles as ranked by Mediabase for the week of Jan 6, 2015 in mp3 320 CBR Stereo.
